Description_lang: The leader of the Shado-pan, an order dedicated to protecting Pandaria from the sha, Taran Zhu is a skilled fighter and fearless leader.
AuraDescription_lang: Taran Zhu is a master of speed, agility, and strength.

description_blz.en_US: The leader of the Shado-pan, an order dedicated to protecting Pandaria from the sha, Taran Zhu is a skilled fighter and fearless leader.
description_blz.es_MX: Taran Zhu, el líder del Shadopan, una orden dedicada a proteger Pandaria de los sha, es un combatiente experto y un líder valeroso.
description_blz.pt_BR: Líder do Shado-Pan, uma ordem dedicada a proteger Pandária contra os sha, Taran Zhu é um guerreiro habilidoso e um líder destemido.
description_blz.de_DE: Taran Zhu, Anführer der Shado-Pan, einem Orden, der sich dem Schutz von Pandaria vor dem Sha gewidmet hat, ist ein fähiger Kämpfer und furchtloser Feldherr.
description_blz.en_GB: The leader of the Shado-pan, an order dedicated to protecting Pandaria from the sha, Taran Zhu is a skilled fighter and fearless leader.

description_blz.fr_FR: Chef de l’ordre des Pandashan qui se consacre à la protection de la Pandarie contre la menace des sha, Taran Zhu est connu pour être un combattant aguerri doublé d’un commandant courageux.

description_blz.ru_RU: Тажань Чжу – лидер ордена Шадо-Пан, защитников Пандарии от ша. Это бесстрашный командир и опытный воин.
description_blz.ko_KR: 최선을 다해 판다리아를 샤의 위협으로부터 수호하고자 한 음영파의 수장 타란 주는 노련한 전사이며 두려움을 모르는 지도자입니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 身為影潘的領導者，一生致力於保護潘達利亞免於煞的腐化，塔蘭‧祝成為技巧精湛的戰士與無畏的領袖。
description_blz.zh_CN: 祝踏岚带领着影踪派努力保护潘达利亚不受煞的侵害，他是一名技艺非凡的勇士，也是一位无畏的领袖。
